name: ITChimes
overview:
IT Chimes is a leading web development and application solutions provider from India. With a satisfied customer list of 120 and a bag full of 300 websites, IT Chimes serves clients from all over the world including USA, UK and India.

Among the solutions, IT Chimes offers website design and development, web & mobile app development for various popular platforms, Database management (DBMS). IT Chimes also allows customers to hire from its talented and experienced programmers in the fields of PHP, .Net and others.

You can subscribe to the newsletter for latest web development trends, tips & tricks, expert talks and free guides. You can further contact for a FREE ASSESSMENT of your site by the experts.
